# PLAYER::CLEAR_PLAYER_HAS_DAMAGED_AT_LEAST_ONE_NON_ANIMAL_PED

## Summary
Call this once before you start checking HAS_PLAYER_DAMAGED_AT_LEAST_ONE_NON_ANIMAL_PED

## Parameters
* **PLAYER_INDEX** player

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
